            "Subject": "Concrete, raking light",
            "Year": "2024",
            "Process": "Pigment print",
            "Edition": "Open"
          },
          "body": "Plate 22 is the only one in the series for which the photographer kept the contact sheet. The frame was the seventh of nine made that afternoon, and it is in many respects the simplest. The light was raking, the surface had been undisturbed."
        },
        {
          "runninghead": "MONOGRAPH NO. 11 · S. ARDEN · DRIFT",
