          "body": "Plate 9 corresponds to day nine of the twelve-day working period. The light was diffuse, the river was nearly still, and the boat was anchored for the first time during the project. The photographer noted that this was the only frame she knew was a photograph at the moment of the shutter."
        },
        {
          "runninghead": "MONOGRAPH NO. 18 · E. SOLBAKKEN · HOUR BLUE",
