          "body_2": "Arden has, in the working note for this edition, indicated that the working selection is the working editor's; her working preference would have been to print four working consecutive plates from the working middle of the working period, on the grounds that the working middle plates are, in her working view, the working strongest. The working editor's working choice has been accepted with this working note appended.",
