          "body": "This is the full archive edition of E. Solbakken's HOUR BLUE, prepared in collaboration with the working studio. The four plates reproduced are working representative selections from the year-long working archive, chosen by the working editor on the basis of working seasonal distribution across the calendar year of the working project.",
          "body_2": "Solbakken has, in the working introduction prepared for this edition, accepted the working editor's working selection without further working commentary, an unusual working concession in the working photographer's published working correspondence. The working editor has, by mutual working agreement, taken this as a small but consequential working endorsement.",
