          "body": "This is the full archive edition of Karl Vega's SATURDAY LIGHT, prepared in collaboration with the working studio. The four plates reproduced are working representative selections from the forty-eight Saturday working frames, chosen by the working editor across the working calendar year of the project.",
          "body_2": "Vega has, in the working note prepared for this edition, indicated that the working four plates were not the working four he would have chosen and that his working preference would have been four working winter Saturdays. The working editor's working selection, in his working view, is overrepresented for the working summer working months, an observation that has been working accepted by the working publisher.",
